name: Meet-madii
body:
### Welcome 
I have created Meet-Madii as a way to put my resume online, while showcasing my love of programming. You can clone my repo like so:
```
$ git clone https://github.com/mammas/Meet-Madii
```
Please check out the hosted site at http://meetmadii.ddns.net
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
